text: Małgorzata Wysocka (born 15 June 1979) is a road cyclist from Poland. She represented her nation at the 2004 Summer Olympics. She also rode at the 1998, 2001, 2003 and 2004 UCI Road World Championships. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Procyclingstats.com Category:1979 births Category:Polish female cyclists Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Lublin Category:Cyclists at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of Poland
